    <item>
      <title>拜登将访问安哥拉和德国，这是他退出大选后的首次出访</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/biden-to-visit-angola-germany-in-first-trip-since-exiting-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登计划十月份访问非洲，并先行前往德国，以履行卸任前访问非洲大陆的承诺，并向华盛顿表明非洲大陆的重要性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/biden-to-visit-angola-germany-in-first-trip-since-exiting-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 19:00:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌拉圭左翼党承诺若赢得大选将实现财政盈余</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/uruguay-s-left-party-pledges-fiscal-surplus-if-it-wins-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据乌拉圭反对党广泛阵线的总统候选人亚曼杜·奥尔西 (Yamandu Orsi) 挑选的财政部长候选人、经济学家加布里埃尔·奥多内 (Gabriel Oddone) 透露，如果他赢得 10 月份的选举，乌拉圭领先的总统候选人亚曼杜·奥尔西 (Yamandu Orsi) 将力争在其任期结束前实现初步财政盈余，并可能缩小该国的通胀目标区间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/uruguay-s-left-party-pledges-fiscal-surplus-if-it-wins-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 18:51:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2023 年雪佛龙向非洲石油国家支付的费用超过向美国支付的费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/chevron-cvx-paid-more-in-tax-to-african-petrostates-than-us-in-2023</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雪佛龙公司2023年向尼日利亚、安哥拉和赤道几内亚缴纳了62.5亿美元的税款和石油产量分成，是该公司向美国政府缴纳金额的三倍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/chevron-cvx-paid-more-in-tax-to-african-petrostates-than-us-in-2023</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 18:48:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列与真主党战争蔓延之际，伊朗新领导人登上联合国舞台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/iran-s-new-leader-takes-un-stage-as-israel-hezbollah-war-spreads</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗总统马苏德·佩泽什基安周二在纽约首次出席联合国大会，提出两项紧迫但相互矛盾的任务：缓解伊朗的经济孤立，同时应对以色列与真主党不断升级的战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/iran-s-new-leader-takes-un-stage-as-israel-hezbollah-war-spreads</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 18:47:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟气候专员谴责中国补贴行为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/eu-climate-czar-calls-out-china-on-climate-industry-subsidies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟气候负责人表示，欧盟不会允许中国在向清洁经济转型期间向市场投放廉价产品，从而威胁欧盟的产业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/eu-climate-czar-calls-out-china-on-climate-industry-subsidies</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 18:01:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普誓言在佐治亚州集会期间抢走其他国家的就业机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/trump-vows-to-take-other-countries-jobs-in-manufacturing-pitch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国前总统唐纳德·特朗普在一次旨在缓解选民对就业和工资担忧的经济讲话中誓言，将利用税收优惠和关税威胁说服外国公司将业务转移到美国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/trump-vows-to-take-other-countries-jobs-in-manufacturing-pitch</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 17:44:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党全国委员会官员称马克·罗宾逊需要反驳“黑纳粹”报告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/rnc-chair-says-onus-on-robinson-to-disprove-black-nazi-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[共和党全国委员会联合主席迈克尔·沃特利周二表示，北卡罗来纳州州长候选人马克·罗宾逊如果想继续参加竞选，就需要证明自己无罪，否认自己在成人网站上发表粗鲁和种族主义言论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/rnc-chair-says-onus-on-robinson-to-disprove-black-nazi-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 17:37:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据报道，抨击桑托斯的纽约议员已将情人纳入工资单</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/ny-congressman-who-blasted-santos-faces-scrutiny-over-payroll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约州众议员安东尼·德斯波西托对乔治·桑托斯的批评毫不留情，他称这位长岛共和党同僚是国会的“污点”，不适合为选民服务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/ny-congressman-who-blasted-santos-faces-scrutiny-over-payroll</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 17:32:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列力争不打地面战就击退真主党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/israel-aims-to-force-back-hezbollah-without-starting-lebanon-ground-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[过去一周，以色列每天都对黎巴嫩境内的真主党发动袭击 —— 从暗杀指挥官到摧毁导弹发射器 —— 官员们表示，以色列此举意在迫使该组织从边境撤退，并停止火箭弹袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/israel-aims-to-force-back-hezbollah-without-starting-lebanon-ground-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 13:20:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列袭击黎巴嫩真主党 造成 500 多人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/israel-s-bombing-of-hezbollah-targets-kills-hundreds-in-lebanon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列对真主党目标进行了更多空袭，这是自 2006 年双方爆发灾难性战争以来，以色列对黎巴嫩实施的最严重、伤亡最惨重的轰炸。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/israel-s-bombing-of-hezbollah-targets-kills-hundreds-in-lebanon</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 09:05:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
